{"type": "article", "id": 14955, "title": "25 个刻奇的句子证明你是一个刻奇的人 |每天还有一个list", "description": "自我感动及感伤，难以拒绝的自我感动和感伤，啊，人生。", "date": "2015-09-26T08:10:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 125, "name": "List"}, {"id": 11405, "name": "好奇心研究所"}], "category": 5, "column": 33, "author": 1288, "comment_count": 19, "praise_count": 174, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607130144LqHSMi832UnKpXvB.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>1.  “愿琴瑟在御，岁月静好。”</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130121VOfuSi6HUGPgbk32.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.73\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>2.  “你若安好，便是晴天。”</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130122UPNRMgB0fajnFDQq.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>3.  “来一场说走就走的旅行。”</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130123eXJ25GZ0aMyQwWFL.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>4.  “世界这么大，我想去看看。”</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130124zH1oAqDtdyU43rY8.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.676\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>5.  “你若盛开，清风自来。”</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071301252fw40XGg5INrZecQ.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.704\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>6.  “不忘初心，方得始终。”</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130126zd43ul8NGSYAQUL6.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>7.  “你若爱，请深爱。”</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071301273YzctBLyAxjq81KF.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.734\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>8.  “愿得一人心，白首不相离。”</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130128amByVPrTnKD153Cp.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>9.  “你的孤独，虽败犹荣。”</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130128CWkdpXvY4EOsabRV.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.56179775\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>10.  “停下脚步，等一等灵魂。”</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060713012973qMgjfnmCdelkoR.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>11.  “就算全世界与你为敌。”</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130131FfBR2A3moWI87Nsr.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.54\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>12.  “心有猛虎，细嗅蔷薇。”</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071301328FgPfYqz2QStu6AC.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.522\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>13.  “灵魂和身体，总有一个在路上。”</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071301331CTirEgB4cxH3D6j.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>14.  “执子之手，与子偕老。”</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130134zQ7rXRDUvtwlVFBf.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>15.  “趁你还在。趁我还爱，请不要说拜拜。”</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130134dP8YnzTCtpsFibvy.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.774\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>16.  “只要你不放手，我永远不说再见。”</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130135Clcp8UJgsPDKfwGX.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>17.  “世间安得双全法，不负如来不负卿。”</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130136N8fnzZLc0tFq1aIO.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.63125\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>18.  “安之若素，莫忘初心。”</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130137TZ85CvBMltPg367b.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"1.00502513\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>19.  “从你的全世界路过。”</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071301386alwvm5LtPZo0DNY.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.564\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>20.  “十年生死枇杷树，若只如初不是云。”</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130139fQGBr8icYwWJHoOV.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>21.  “我向前一步，然后遇到了你。”</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130140XS5PaDiF2OJMpmfg.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>22.  “知足常乐，但求平凡。”</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130141ujm8x51tUB6GyTq0.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>23.  “七年前我喝了你酿的一杯酒，我醉到了今天。”</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130141gXzFuQ7AsSCBYIcj.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.56410256\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>24.  “青春。。少年。。儿时。。寂静。。完满。。恬淡。。天空。。远方。。”</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130142JNhUluFEaz8WPgAw.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>25.  以及一切哈佛大学图书馆格言校训系列……</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130143f5BdxgoRMDJ2Z9WK.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.456\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}